<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - QRCraft by Meecro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }
        
        :root {
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --primary-light: #3b82f6;
            --secondary: #0ea5e9;
            --accent: #8b5cf6;
            --dark: #0f172a;
            --darker: #020617;
            --light: #f1f5f9;
            --lighter: #f8fafc;
            --gray: #94a3b8;
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--darker), var(--dark));
            color: var(--light);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }
        
        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .header-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .logo-icon {
            background: var(--primary);
            width: 2.8rem;
            height: 2.8rem;
            border-radius: 0.8rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
        }
        
        .logo-icon i {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .logo-text {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .logo-text span {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-light), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .app-icon-large {
            width: 6rem;
            height: 6rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #283593);
            border-radius: 1.2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 2px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
        }
        
        .app-icon-large i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #a78bfa;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--light);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .hero .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .last-updated {
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 3px;
            width: 5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            margin: 1.5rem auto;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        /* Policy Content */
        .policy-content {
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .policy-intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }
        
        .policy-intro p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .policy-section {
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }
        
        .policy-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }
        
        .policy-section h2 i {
            color: var(--accent);
            width: 2.2rem;
            height: 2.2rem;
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .policy-point {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .policy-point h3 {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            color: var(--light);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
        }
        
        .policy-point h3 i {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .policy-point p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-left: 1.8rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
            border-radius: 0.8rem;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            margin: 1.2rem 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box p {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box i {
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-top: 0.2rem;
        }
        
        .third-party {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        
        .third-party-item {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.3);
            border-radius: 0.8rem;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
        }
        
        .third-party-item h4 {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
        }
        
        .third-party-item p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-left: 0;
        }
        
        .contact-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
            margin: 2.5rem 0;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--accent);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }
        
        .contact-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }
        
        .contact-email {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin: 1.2rem 0;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            border-radius: 3rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
        }
        
        .contact-email:hover {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        /* Buttons */
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn i {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .footer-logo span {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-light), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .footer-tagline {
            color: var(--gray);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.8rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--light);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        
        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--secondary);
        }
        
        .copyright {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--gray);
        }
        
        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header-inner {
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }
            
            .hero {
                padding: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            
            .policy-section {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .policy-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            
            .policy-point h3 {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .policy-point p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                margin-left: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .contact-email {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .app-icon-large {
                width: 5rem;
                height: 5rem;
            }
            
            .app-icon-large i {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .logo-text {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
            
            .hero .subtitle {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            
            .policy-section {
                padding: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .policy-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .policy-point h3 {
                font-size: 1.05rem;
            }
            
            .policy-point p {
                margin-left: 1.2rem;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
            
            .third-party {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .contact-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .contact-email {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }
            
            .footer-links {
                gap: 1.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-inner">
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="logo-text">Meecro<span>Dev</span></div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="app-icon-large">
                <i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i>
            </div>
            <h1>Privacy Policy for QRCraft</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your privacy matters. This policy explains how we handle your information in our QR code scanning and generation app.</p>
            <div class="last-updated">
                <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Last Updated: May 21, 2025
            </div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="policy-intro">
                <p>This Privacy Policy explains how QRCraft collects, uses, and protects your information. By using QRCraft, you agree to this policy.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Information We Collect -->
            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-database"></i> Information We Collect</h2>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-camera"></i> Camera Access</h3>
                    <p>Required solely for scanning QR codes. No images or video are stored or transmitted.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> Generated QR Codes</h3>
                    <p>Data you input to generate QR codes (e.g., URLs, text) is processed locally and never uploaded to our servers.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Scan History</h3>
                    <p>Saved locally on your device (optional) and never shared externally.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-ad"></i> AdMob Data</h3>
                    <p>Google AdMob may collect anonymized data (device ID, IP address) for personalized ads, as per Google's policies.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- How We Use Information -->
            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> How We Use Information</h2>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> QR Functionality</h3>
                    <p>Camera access is used in real-time for scanning; generated QR data remains on your device unless you choose to share it.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-ad"></i> Advertising</h3>
                    <p>AdMob serves non-intrusive ads (banner and interstitial) using standard ad-serving technologies.</p>
                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <p><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> We use carefully placed ads to support development while maintaining a positive user experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Third-Party Services -->
            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> Third-Party Services</h2>
                
                <div class="third-party">
                    <div class="third-party-item">
                        <h4><i class="fab fa-google"></i> Google AdMob</h4>
                        <p>Follows Google's Privacy Policy. We only use AdMob for ad serving in our free version.</p>
                        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="btn" style="margin-top: 0.8rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> View Policy
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="third-party-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-code"></i> ZXing Library</h4>
                        <p>Open-source QR scanning library. Does not collect any user data.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Data Security -->
            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Data Security</h2>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <p>All user-generated data (scan history, QR codes) is stored locally and can be cleared via the app's "Clear History" feature.</p>
                    <p>We do not sell, share, or transmit your data to third parties beyond what's necessary for ad serving through Google AdMob.</p>
                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <p><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Your generated QR codes and scan history never leave your device and are not accessible by us or any third parties.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Children's Privacy -->
            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-child"></i> Children's Privacy</h2>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <p>QRCraft complies with COPPA (Children's Online Privacy Protection Act). We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Policy Changes -->
            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Policy Updates</h2>
                
                <div class="policy-point">
                    <p>Updates to this policy will be posted on this page. Continued use of the app signifies your acceptance of any changes.</p>
                    <p>We will notify users of significant changes through app updates or in-app notifications.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Contact Section -->
            <div class="contact-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</h2>
                <p>For any questions about this privacy policy or your data:</p>
                <a href="mailto:c.g.s.hassan.ali@gmail.com" class="contact-email">
                    <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> c.g.s.hassan.ali@gmail.com
                </a>
                <p>We typically respond within 24-48 hours.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-logo">Meecro<span>Dev</span></div>
            <p class="footer-tagline">Transparent development for privacy-conscious users</p>
            
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> GitHub</a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Developer</a>
                <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i> Terms</a>
            </div>
            
            <p class="copyright">© 2023 Meecro Development. All rights reserved.<br>QRCraft and all related content are properties of Meecro.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
